      <title>卡多佐预计尼日利亚汇款将增至 120 亿美元：Thisday</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/cardoso-sees-nigeria-remittances-rising-to-12-billion-thisday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《今日报》报道，尼日利亚央行行长奥拉耶米·卡多佐表示，尼日利亚有信心每月吸引海外公民汇款 10 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/cardoso-sees-nigeria-remittances-rising-to-12-billion-thisday</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 07:25:44 GMT</pubDate>
