    <item>
      <title>美联储政策会议前将公布国内生产总值和受风暴影响的就业数据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-26/gdp-storm-impacted-jobs-numbers-to-set-table-ahead-of-fed-policy-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[距美联储官员开会讨论适当的降息节奏还有一周时间，三份备受瞩目的报告预计将显示美国经济的潜在弹性和就业增长的暂时停滞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-26/gdp-storm-impacted-jobs-numbers-to-set-table-ahead-of-fed-policy-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 26 Oct 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券交易狂潮可能给做市商带来虚假的安全感</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-26/bond-trading-frenzy-risks-giving-market-makers-a-false-sense-of-security</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从表面上看，公司债券市场从未如此稳定和流动。在美国，9 月份的交易量创下了有史以来的最高纪录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-26/bond-trading-frenzy-risks-giving-market-makers-a-false-sense-of-security</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 26 Oct 2024 18:37:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登首次就以色列空袭发表讲话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-26/biden-gives-first-remarks-on-israeli-airstrikes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登总统首次就以色列周六凌晨对伊朗发动的一系列空袭作出回应。他说，美国事先得到了空袭通知，根据美国情报部门的说法，“看起来他们没有击中除军事目标以外的任何目标。”（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-26/biden-gives-first-remarks-on-israeli-airstrikes</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 26 Oct 2024 18:29:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高级官员称中国刺激计划旨在促进消费</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-26/china-s-stimulus-aims-to-boost-consumption-top-official-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部副部长廖岷表示，中国近期推出的刺激政策主要围绕扩大内需和实现国家年度增长目标。投资者正在等待全国人大会议公布中国政府关键财政刺激方案的细节。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-26/china-s-stimulus-aims-to-boost-consumption-top-official-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 26 Oct 2024 03:31:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
